divs: Sighting DetailsWas driving thru town, noticed the clouds around the sun turned rainbowish, took a few pictures of the sun, then took a few more of the scenery. Upon developing the picture, I noticed a silver triangle type object in the top right. When zoomed in, the object appears to have three balls of light on the bottom. Not sure if it is dust from the windshield, but it seems to be catching the light from the sun.
